animeTitle: Paper Cranes Story: Kenta to Maiko
animeDescription: Based on the picture eBook of the same name.One by one, with feeling, the Thousand Paper Cranes are folded.What if, those paper cranes had a "life" of their own...The purpose given to the Thousand Paper Cranes!The spectacular adventure of Kenta and Maiko begins now!!(Source: dreamonefilm)
